Uber talented artist, BM Baby has dropped one of the most mood lifting songs titled “BABA”. The Afro juice artist believes with so much creative process she puts into her craft will surely create wide acceptance for her and her music. The single BABA fascinates good music lovers worldwide. Her music style embodies a mix of Dancehall, RnB, Afro and Soul and a musical cocktail for the soul. Real name Bertha Mary Okey, but popularly called BM Baby started her singing career at a very tender age from school doubling up also as a chorister in church after which she moved on to become a professional singer and actress. She schooled in the prestigious Benue state university, with a diploma in mass communication. And also has a B.s.c in political science at the National Open University. The new single BABA is available on all streaming platforms.